  "conclusion": "Explicit c2 batched_lm_head with the full-hidden final-cast stabilizer (requested 999999, clamped to 2048) was green across 20 reproducible explicit runs, including four c8\u2192c2 cycles, with native_row_aware_lm_head=true and empty sampler blockers. A temporary no-flag promotion candidate using the same stabilizer nevertheless reproduced the historical row0/token82 flake once in 8 runs, and a subsequent serial no-flag active verify transiently printed 104 before three recovery repeats and the final active verify returned to 137. Therefore c2 is not promoted this iteration; the no-flag default remains serial_lm_head. This is sampler-stability runtime evidence only and makes no retained throughput/scaling claim.",
